Synergy CHC Corp.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 28, 2017 6:43 PM ET
Personal Products

Company Overview of Synergy CHC Corp.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Synergy CHC Corp., a consumer health care company, markets and distributes various consumer branded products primarily in the health and wellness industry in the United States and internationally. The company offers FOCUSfactor, a brain-health nutritional supplement that includes a proprietary blend of brain supporting vitamins, minerals, antioxidants, and other nutrients; Flat Tummy Tea, a two-step herbal detox tea that works to help speed metabolism, boost energy, and reduce bloating; and Hand MD, an anti-aging skincare line formulated specifically for the hands. It also provides Neuragen, a topical product that works directly at the site of the pain as opposed to oral products; and Urgent...
Synergy CHC Corp., a consumer health care company, markets and distributes various consumer branded products primarily in the health and wellness industry in the United States and internationally. The company offers FOCUSfactor, a brain-health nutritional supplement that includes a proprietary blend of brain supporting vitamins, minerals, antioxidants, and other nutrients; Flat Tummy Tea, a two-step herbal detox tea that works to help speed metabolism, boost energy, and reduce bloating; and Hand MD, an anti-aging skincare line formulated specifically for the hands. It also provides Neuragen, a topical product that works directly at the site of the pain as opposed to oral products; and UrgentRx, a fast acting flavored powdered medication for immediate relief of every day ailments such as allergy attacks, headaches, aches and pains, heartburn, and upset stomach. The company was formerly known as Synergy Strips Corp. and changed its name to Synergy CHC Corp. in August 2015. Synergy CHC Corp. was founded in 2012 and is based in Westbrook, Maine.
