			Company Description 
		


                Synergy CHC Corp. is a consumer health care company. It engages in the marketing and distribution of consumer-branded products through various distribution channels in the health and wellness industry. The company was founded on December 29, 2010 and is headquartered in Westbrook, ME.
            




