Story
Synergy is a portfolio of consumer health care and wellness
brands leading the way in their respective industries. 





Strategy
A category leading & value enhancing group of brands on a mission to find powerful & proven products in the health 
space & build a portfolio of companies who make lives brighter & better.




OurBrands


01 FOCUS FACTOR


02 FLAT TUMMY TEA


03 HAND – MD


04 PER-FéKT BEAUTY


05 SNEAKY VAUNT


 See All 











01






FOCUS FACTOR
Clinically proven and America’s #1 Brain Health Supplement for Over 10 years.
Visit website 




FLAT TUMMY TEA
Global dominating and social media sensation 2-step detox tea.
Visit website 




HAND – MD
Clinically proven and the only all-natural anti-aging hand product on the market.
Visit website 




PER-FéKT BEAUTY
Specialized range of beauty products (makeup, skin-care & body).
Visit website 




SNEAKY VAUNT
From the team that brought you Flat Tummy Tea, Sneaky Vaunt keeps you damn good looking 24/7.
Visit website 







Mission Statement:
Brighter and Better Lives
For Synergy CHC, the statement “Brighter & Better Lives” represents the commitment to a lasting footprint of health. We are a consumer health care company dedicated to revenue growth but beyond sales, our brands are the heroes & we will be measured by their reputation. A Synergy brand will help consumers find the brighter & better life they desire in proven & tangible ways. As we grow, we intend to leave a footprint of health & wellness in North America and beyond.
Partnerwith us






Approach
For us, Innovation isn’t just a buzz word. Drawing on the decades of experience from a team who understands the health sector intimately, we deliver a powerful, unique & proprietary innovation engine to each of our brands. From this, we achieve rapid bottom line growth & brand awareness through an Omni-channel approach.








The Team
We are built by a leadership team with decades of entrepreneurial success and industry expertise. In just under two years, Synergy has experienced explosive growth with excellent landmark acquisitions and Omni-channel revenue growth.
VIEWLEADERSHIP










