Brands
Synergy CHC’s growth strategy has seen strategic acquisitions across
proven and tested brands in Nutraceuticals, Cosmeceuticals, Beauty and
Marketing Tech. As we accelerate and expand our footprint with this
ever-growing portfolio of brands that belong to Synergy, our strategy
remains the same. Find brands doing good and incorporate cutting
edge strategies to accelerate their growth. 



